snippet.title: MEETUPVIDEO
snippet.description: Meetupvideo Ltd. is an industry-leading video production company with over 16 years of experience in live streaming, video recording, IT solutions, and consulting. We pride ourselves in delivering impeccably high-quality services for business and personal use, which are available throughout the world. We are a reliable family business that values inclusion and diversity. Our mission is to record anything you feel should stay around for generations to come because if it is dear to you, it is dear to us.
